title: Talaat Dahshan
text: Talaat Dahshan (born 7 June 1943) is an Egyptian <a href="boxing">boxer</a>. He competed in the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%201968%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Heavyweight">men's heavyweight</a> event at the <a href="1968%20Summer%20Olympics">1968 Summer Olympics</a>.
